StringValues.16: A note from Nasun ibn Tifar and Ahyara in the Yaraq Outposts, for delivery to Mara al-Luq outside Yaraq.
StringValues.15: A note from Nasun ibn Tifar and Ahyara for delivery to Mara al-Luq.

Pages.Text:
Lovely Mara,

We have had news of fortune's munificence to you.  Accept our compliments in this happy time.

- Nasun ibn Tifar

What he said.

- Ahyara
